    "blog.cat.community":"Our Community",
    "blog.p7.title":"The 'Little Jaguar of the Amazon' Spent the Weekend at Vista do Lago",
    "blog.p7.excerpt":"Yandra Mawé, the six-year-old indigenous star the internet calls the 'Oncinha do Amazonas', came to visit us — and the video from her stay is going viral.",
    "blog.p7.meta":"July 2026 · 3 min read",
